{"tid":391722,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"放鳥被譙！17歲女「喝威士忌+啤酒」站不穩見網友…遭輪流性侵","createTime":"2017-09-08T03:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T08:27:03.000Z","uid":122,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ac5381269b5dfc7b81eed16e1702bb71e23d645","tid":391722,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T03:57:22.000Z","msg":"<strong>放鳥被譙！17歲女「喝威士忌+啤酒」站不穩見網友&hellip;遭輪流性侵</strong><br />\n<br />\n新北市一名17歲少女小美（化名）喝得爛醉，依舊要赴陳姓網友的約，結果被對方及其李姓友人先後性侵。新北地方法院判陳、李各3年徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n判決指出，小美2016年初透過臉書認識陳男（19歲），雙方聊天聊了一、二周，相約同年2月10日在板橋火車站見面；但她放鳥對方，跟友人到台北松山彩虹橋烤肉，喝下好幾瓶啤酒和半瓶伏特加。<br />\n<br />\n小美當下醉到站不穩，但看到陳男在臉書痛罵自己，覺得很不好意思，走路搖搖晃晃堅持赴約。陳男騎機車載小美到李姓友人的住處，竟起色心，兩人先後性侵她。法官考量兩人認罪，且各賠小美30、40萬元，達成和解，依乘機性交罪判兩人各3年徒刑。全案可上訴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/VastDisguisedAnophelesmosquito-small.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FVastDisguisedAnophelesmosquito-small.gif&h=f1def05e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47dd9237a5ec8954a47f8669527220df343ddf06","tid":391722,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T03:59:30.000Z","msg":"呢球射得靚"},{"pid":"5403ecf962917054249d2592f8748c8e1f0e5819","tid":391722,"uid":115150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T03:59:53.000Z","msg":"巴哥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb8ca16005a8bd3362305fa21041cd2ba04472c","tid":391722,"uid":33439,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T04:01:33.000Z","msg":"比人屌兩獲就70萬台幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b9f0a908594dccae7212cf48351590069d8cf51","tid":391722,"uid":67392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T04:08:24.000Z","msg":"啲錢真係易搵"},{"pid":"25a46fe06bc3299b67f941b2a9ab81ff9abef52d","tid":391722,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T04:21:46.000Z","msg":"台妺飲到醉訓一覺就70萬<im